name: .XTBL File Extension
summary: Learn about .XTBL files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: There is currently no known way to restore XTBl files to their original state. The best ways to retrieve your files are either to recover them from a recent backup or perform a full System Restore to a point before your computer was infected.
